  "texts": [
    "These hypotheses are then passed to the Modifi-cation Agent, which synthesizes changes to agent logic, interactions, or dependencies, producing new system variants.",
    "The Execution Agent executes the newly modified versions of the system, and performance metrics are gathered.",
    "The outputs generated are evaluated using qualitative and quantitative criteria (e.g., clarity, relevance, execution time).",
    "The Selection Agent compares the newly generated outputs against the best-known variant, ranks the variants, and determines whether the new output is superior.",
    "Memory Module stores the bestperforming variants for future iterations."
  ],
